-- Samsung Raises Flat-Panel TV Sales Target to as Many as 50 Million Sets
-- Sungwoo Park
-- 2010-07-06T03:53:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-06/samsung-raises-flat-panel-tv-sales-target-to-as-many-as-50-million-sets.html

          
          
             Samsung Electronics Co., the world’s
largest television maker, raised this year’s target for global
flat-panel television sales to as many as 50 million units on
increased demand.  
 The Suwon, South Korea-based company previously aimed to
sell 39 million units in 2010, James Chung, a company spokesman,
said today by phone.  
